# 🔗 03 — Vendor Risk Assessment

> **Framework:** ISO 27001 &nbsp;|&nbsp; **Questions:** 20 across 5 domains &nbsp;|&nbsp; **Output:** Low / Medium / High risk rating

---

## Overview

A professional 20-question vendor security questionnaire for evaluating third-party vendors before granting access to company systems or customer data. Includes a completed sample assessment with full risk rating narrative.

Third-party vendor risk is one of the fastest-growing threat vectors — vendors with weak security postures represent a significant risk to any organization's compliance and data protection program. This questionnaire operationalizes that risk evaluation process.

