## Risk Rating Methodology

| Score Range | Rating | Action Required |
|---|---|---|
| 85–100 | 🟢 **Low** | Approve vendor; standard annual review |
| 65–84 | 🟡 **Medium** | Approve with conditions; remediation plan required within 60 days |
| 0–64 | 🔴 **High** | Do not approve until critical findings remediated; re-assess |

